@Ambev.DeveloperEvaluation.WebApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5119

### Create sale
POST {{Ambev.DeveloperEvaluation.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "saleNumber": "SALE-001",
  "saleDate": "2026-06-01T10:00:00Z",
  "customer": { "id": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6", "name": "Acme Corp" },
  "branch": { "id": "4fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa7", "name": "Downtown" },
  "items": [
    {
      "product": { "id": "5fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa8", "name": "Beer 600ml" },
      "quantity": 5,
      "unitPrice": 10.00
    }
  ]
}

### Get sale by id
GET {{Ambev.DeveloperEvaluation.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/sales/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### List sales
GET {{Ambev.DeveloperEvaluation.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/sales?_page=1&_size=10&_order=saleDate desc

### List sales with filters
GET {{Ambev.DeveloperEvaluation.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/sales?SaleNumber=SALE*&Customer=Acme&_minTotalAmount=10&_maxTotalAmount=500
